      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>851</offset>
        <text>In our simulation of future ocean conditions, we find an undersaturation with respect to carbonate in the deep ocean that exceeds that experienced during the Palaeocene-Eocene thermal maximum and could endanger calcifying organisms.
</text>
        <annotation id="T15">
          <infon key="brat-id">T15</infon>
