      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">8</infon>
        <offset>1084</offset>
        <text>Furthermore, our simulations show higher rates of environmental change at the surface for the future than the Palaeocene-Eocene thermal maximum, which could potentially challenge the ability of plankton to adapt.
</text>
